                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Athens</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-06-15"><hi rend="italic">June 15,
                                1903</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            <seg rendition="#left">Servian series.]</seg></opener>
                        <p>Peter Karageorgevitch proclaimed King. All quiet Belgrade.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi></signed></closer>
